data.description: Welcome Home to Taylor Plantation! This is a beautifully maintained single-story gem. Positioned on a spacious corner lot, it offers ample yard space and privacy in the back with a 6 foot fence. Whether you prefer relaxing on the outdoor patio, or unwinding on the screened-in porch this home has it all.When you step inside you'll be greeted by inviting archways, high ceilings and a generously sized family room. The kitchen boasts a substantial island, luxurious leathered granite countertops, 42-inch cabinets, and high-end stainless steel appliances.
